data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 2021 built home; like new!! in the heart of Winn Ridge. Larger 5 bedroom house + study!! with very good size secondary bedrooms, this home will always be brighter than others the way of its construction. The large entry way opens to a spacious family room with bright windows looking out to the massive back patio.Open concept family, dining, has plenty of room for entertaining or relaxing after a long day. The large social island will be a favorite gathering spot in this home. This thoughtful design features split bedrooms, a walk-in pantry and a spacious utility room, you really could not ask for anything more. The 3 additional bedrooms are located on the second floor along with a bonus gameroom. This two story gem has everything you want which makes it a perfect place to settle into, with an oversized backyard situated in a corner lot offering the perfect summer cookouts and festivities throughout the year!!
